      "description": "URIB Stack \u2014 Universal Rail Integration Bridge. Implements the full 7-stage pipeline from the URIB Math Set spec: canonical tokenization (h_D), semantic graph (h_G), ThreadZero truth chain (T*), stack commitment (C_stack), Bitcoin Taproot anchoring, cross-rail mapping (BTC/XRP/ISO/CBDC), and ISO 20022 pacs.008 settlement emission. Use action='orchestrate' for the full pipeline, 'emit_iso' for a standalone ISO 20022 message, 'verify' to check a stack commitment."
